==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interseptal
<hw>In`ter*sep"tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Biol.)</fld>
<def>Between septa; <as>as, the <ex>interseptal</ex> spaces or zones,
between the transparent, or septal, zones in striated muscle; the
<ex>interseptal</ex> chambers of a shell, or of a seed
vessel.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intersert</ent>⟦br⟧
